Hey BGSA,

Thanks to everyone who came out to the Holiday Party and made it a great night! Also a BIG thanks to all the organizers!

Please save the date for our **Welcome Back** Event at Thomson House in the New Year featuring nachos and drinks. And if any of you are heading home for the holidays, we wish you all safe travels and happy holidays! We will send out one last BGSA Weekly of the year next week.

Don't forget to check out our room.  Just contact a key holder to so you can drop in or book the room for a meeting using our calendar: [http://www.brownbearsw.com/cal/bgsa-room-booking](http://www.brownbearsw.com/cal/bgsa-room-booking)

For more information on key holder locations:
[http://mcgillbgsa.com/bgsaroom/](http://mcgillbgsa.com/bgsaroom/)



